{"tid":2071614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：根據英國做法　「勾結」外國制裁屬「恐怖主義」","createTime":"2020-06-20T03:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T06:18:36.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"f4fa169cc9f6ccfd66345964ea582b74b0b420ab","tid":2071614,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:40:08.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊認為在港區國安法下，叫香港官員下台不等於顛覆政權，又表示顛覆政權是將整個制度改變。他舉例說，有人對官員不滿而要求他下台，之後有另一人上任同一崗位，只是換人，並不構成顛覆。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊在電台節目表示，「干預」是屬於中性，是從外部影響香港，而「勾結」的意思負面，是從內至外，性質較嚴重，會涉及刑事罪行。對於勾結外國勢力制裁香港是否違法，他認為制裁香港不是分裂國家，亦無顛覆香港制度，但根據英國做法，影響經濟就屬恐怖主義，因此要視乎條文寫法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533127-20200620.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533127-20200620.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=9ec3d0bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533127-20200620.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0d91f32d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533127-20200620.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f31fbe1987498705cc57e53a08a321e4b657f7","tid":2071614,"uid":132587,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:41:51.000Z","msg":"中共本身已經係個恐怖主義既國家<br />\n同埋唔好下下都覺得勾結啦<br />\n你做錯野 其他人個個都走出黎話你錯 咁又叫勾結咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae9be649d56aca724bde6a5b4ac7369a0784039","tid":2071614,"uid":189157,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:44:06.000Z","msg":"咁淚曬雪廠街係咪分裂國家"},{"pid":"151b49a0d7dda8ef61a1fb567d847986b9433fb3","tid":2071614,"uid":58630,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"r